Package: webhost
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, php, python, npm, ngrok, cloudflared, figlet, openssh
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/WebHost
Description: Serve local directories and expose via tunnels
 WebHost is a Bash script that starts a local web server (PHP, Python,
 or Node.js) and tunnels it to the internet using TunnelMole, Localhost.run,
 Cloudflared, or Ngrok. It provides an interactive menu, color output,
 and automatic cleanup. Ideal for testing webhooks, sharing development
 servers, or exposing local services.
